<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />The righteous will also see it and fear;</para>

<para style="q1">they will laugh at him and say,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />"See, this is a man who did not make God his refuge,</para>

<para style="q1">but he trusted in the abundance of his wealth,</para>

<para style="q1">and he was strong when he destroyed others."</para>
